# EmailJS (browser) — used for Contact, Volunteer, Events, and Messaging forms.
# Create a service + template at https://www.emailjs.com/ ; set the template "To" to erik@patriotsinaction.com (or your inbox).
# Default app payload matches a “Contact Us” template: name, title, message, time (e.g. subject “Contact Us: {{title}}”).
# VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=
# VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=
# VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=
